"    <a class=\"drug drug_general\" href=\"UTD.htm?1/52/1862?source=see_link\">",
"     see \"Topical tretinoin (topical all trans retinoic acid): Drug information\"",
"    </a>",
"    and",
"    <a class=\"drug drug_pediatric\" href=\"UTD.htm?42/10/43171?source=see_link\">",
"     see \"Topical tretinoin (topical all trans retinoic acid): Pediatric drug information\"",
"    </a>",
"    )",
"   </p>",
